The future of Ai was one of civilization's oldest dreams.
Rationaly, our systems actually evolve in an opposite direction which reverses individual improvements to benefit members of the same group.
As the integration and memory chips grow smaller then the fields in robotics will grow larger.
Larger in a routine where we can already create droids, drones and robots along the way.
A question where we could ask ourselves that if we can create machines that can do basic task,
Why can't we make a robot that acts as a human?
Although, empathy may take time to prescribe with more factors to consider when making a decision from a robot.
